The purpose of GA&C is to build an online mueseum that is accessible to everyone.

The GA&C uses technology to digitize what mueseums have been doing for centuries. They are ensuring that human expresion, history, and expression are kept safe for generations to come. They make historical artworks available in a high quality format, to scholars and the world, enabling academic and intellectual discourse on paintings and artworks. The program shows related artworks and allows users to navigate collection in orders that would not be possible to do physically. Using technology they are able to organize works by dominant colour present, timeline and popularity.

The GA&C program is run by the Culture Institute at Google, it is a Not-For-Profit organization. The program is funded by Google and partners with Cultural Intstitutes around the world to share the 
